11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_PLAYOUT_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_PLAYOUT_H_
13
14#include <stdint.h>
15
16#include <memory>
17
18#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
19
20namespace webrtc {
21
22class RtcEventAudioPlayout final : public RtcEvent {
23 public:
24 static constexpr Type kType = Type::AudioPlayout;
25
26 explicit RtcEventAudioPlayout(uint32_t ssrc);
27 ~RtcEventAudioPlayout() override = default;
28
29 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
30 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
31
32 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAudioPlayout> Copy() const;
33
34 uint32_t ssrc() const { return ssrc_; }
35
36 private:
37 RtcEventAudioPlayout(const RtcEventAudioPlayout& other);
38
39 const uint32_t ssrc_;
40};
41
42struct LoggedAudioPlayoutEvent {
43 LoggedAudioPlayoutEvent() = default;
44 LoggedAudioPlayoutEvent(int64_t timestamp_us, uint32_t ssrc)
45 : timestamp_us(timestamp_us), ssrc(ssrc) {}
46
47 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_us; }
48 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_us / 1000; }
49
50 int64_t timestamp_us;
51 uint32_t ssrc;
52};
53
54} // namespace webrtc
55
56#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_PLAYOUT_H_
